'''老韦斯特伯里花园'''（Old Westbury Gardens）位于美国纽约州长岛北海岸[[拿骚县_(纽约州)|拿骚县]][[旧韦斯特伯里_(纽约州)|老韦斯特伯里]]村老韦斯特伯里路71号，原为钢铁大王约翰‧菲利普斯的庄园，1959年菲利普斯去世后向公众开放。

== 历史 ==
[[File:Mrs_Henry_Phipps_and_Her_Grandson_Winston_John_Singer_Sargent_1907.jpeg|thumb]]
庄园由约翰.菲普斯于1903年开始建造。菲力普斯承诺给他的英国未婚妻玛格丽特在美国建造一座和家乡的巴特尔修道院一样的庄园。至1906年完工后，菲力普斯一家入住庄园。<ref name="NysNrhpNom">{{cite web| url = https://cris.parks.ny.gov/| title = Cultural Resource Information System (CRIS)| publisher = New York State Office of Parks, Recreation and Historic Preservation| format = Searchable database| accessdate = 2016-03-01| archive-url = https://archive.today/20150701003048/http://cris.parks.ny.gov/| archive-date = 2015-07-01| dead-url = yes}} ''Note:'' This includes {{cite web| url = https://cris.parks.ny.gov/Uploads/ViewDoc.aspx?mode=A&id=31193&q=false| title = National Register of Historic Places Registration Form: Old Westbury Gardens| accessdate = 2016-03-01| author = Raymond W. Smith| format = PDF| date = July 1976}} and [https://cris.parks.ny.gov/Uploads/ViewDoc.aspx?mode=A&id=31192&q=false ''Accompanying photographs''], {{cite web| url = https://cris.parks.ny.gov/Uploads/ViewDoc.aspx?mode=A&id=31188&q=false| title = National Register of Historic Places Registration Form: Old Westbury Gardens (Boundary Increase)| accessdate = 2016-03-01| author = Lorraine Gilligan| format = PDF| date = 2010年8月}} and [https://cris.parks.ny.gov/Uploads/ViewDoc.aspx?mode=A&id=31190&q=false ''Accompanying photographs'']</ref>

韦斯特伯里庄园为英王查理二世风格，由Geoge A. Crawley设计，有23个房间，占地{{convert|160|acre|km2}}。

[[约翰·辛格·萨金特|约翰·辛格·萨金特]]的油画《亨利·菲普斯夫人和她的孙子温斯顿》悬挂在餐厅。[[温斯顿·丘吉尔|温斯顿·丘吉尔]]是孩子的教父。

